mmj.transforms

Class EquivalenceInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmj.transforms.DBInfo
      • mmj.transforms.EquivalenceInfo

  • public class EquivalenceInfo
extends DBInfo
    This class is used for equivalence transformations.

    Note: Now there is a restriction: the library has to define only one equivalence operator for every type. In set.mm we have 2 types: wff, class.
